+++ b/shenyu-infra/README.md
@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@
+# shenyu-infra
+
+Shared, reusable infrastructure building blocks used across the Shenyu codebase.
+
+## Modules
+
+- `shenyu-infra-http`: factories for common HTTP clients (OkHttp + RestTemplate).
+- `shenyu-infra-zookeeper`: shared Zookeeper config + Curator client factory.
+
+## Usage
+
+Add the corresponding module dependency (and keep using your existing client libraries):
+
+- `org.apache.shenyu:shenyu-infra-http`
+- `org.apache.shenyu:shenyu-infra-zookeeper`
+
+These modules centralize client construction defaults to avoid duplicating configuration logic in multiple places.
+
